headline.main: Native Dancer Takes Belmont Sprint in His First Race Since Last August; 3-20 CHOICE BEATS LAFFANGO EASILY Native Dancer Earnings Rise to $753,670 -- 13 in Chase, 14 in Withers Today

results.snippet: Alfred Gwynne Vanderbilt's Native Dancer made a triumphant return to race-running at Belmont Park yesterday.
results.lead_paragraph: Alfred Gwynne Vanderbilt's Native Dancer made a triumphant return to race-running at Belmont Park yesterday.

headline.main: STRAIGHT FACE 2D; Native Dancer, 1 to 4, Takes Metropolitan at Belmont Park DANCER, 1-4, WINS IN METROPOLITAN

results.snippet: Native Dancer gave weight -- and a beating -- to eight other horses in Belmont Park's Metropolitan Handicap yesterday. The mile run was a five-alarm thriller.
results.lead_paragraph: Native Dancer gave weight -- and a beating -- to eight other horses in Belmont Park's Metropolitan Handicap yesterday. The mile run was a five-alarm thriller.

headline.main: Native Dancer in 2-Mile Gallop; Islander Wins at Belmont Park; VANDERBILT STAR MAY RACE MONDAY Native Dancer Top Weight at 133 Pounds in Suburban at Belmont -- Islander First

results.snippet: A couple of Polynesian's sons figured most prominently in the A. M. and P. M. proceedings at Belmont Park yesterday.
results.lead_paragraph: A couple of Polynesian's sons figured most prominently in the A. M. and P. M. proceedings at Belmont Park yesterday.
